### 📝 Assignment 2-3-2: SafeMap 구현

**요구사항:**
1. map + RWMutex로 구성된 SafeMap 타입 설계
2. Get, Set, Delete, Length, Keys 메서드 구현
3. 여러 고루틴이 동시에 접근 가능 (Race Detector 통과)

**구조체 정의:**
```go
type SafeMap struct {
    mu    sync.RWMutex
    items map[string]interface{}
}

func (sm *SafeMap) Get(key string) (interface{}, bool)
func (sm *SafeMap) Set(key string, value interface{})
func (sm *SafeMap) Delete(key string)
